enable_commands
Discworld efun help
enable_commands

void enable_commands()

.SP 5 5
Enable this object to use commands normally accessible to players.
This also marks the current object as living. Commands defined by player.c 
will not be accessible, of course.

This function must be called if the object is supposed to interact
with other players.

Avoid to call this function from other places then create(), because the
command_giver will be set to the this object.
.EP

See also
.SI 5
command, living.
.EI
